downloadTitle: Microsoft BTS WSE Adapter 3.0 Management Pack for MOM 2005
downloadDescription: Microsoft BTS WSE Adapter 3.0 Management Pack monitors BTS (BizTalk Server) WSE Adapter 3.0 runtime events.
detailsSection:
Microsoft BizTalk Server (BTS) Well Enabled Services (WSE) Adapter 3.0 Management Pack for MOM monitors the BTS WSE Adapter 3.0 services application event log. This management pack is build for monitoring BTS WSE Adapter 3.0 service. The events collected indicate critical issues, informational events and error events generated during various BTS WSE Adapter 3.0 configurations and process flows.

Feature Summary:

BTS WSE Adapter 3.0 services generated Error and Informational events.
Alerts indicating configuration issues with adapter

Release and Update History:

7/14/2006 Original product release date (Version 03.0.0000.0000).
systemRequirementsSection: Microsoft Windows Server™ 2003 Enterprise Edition Service Pack 1 (SP1)
